<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{ basics.name }} - Cover Letter</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Merriweather:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,700;0,900;1,300;1,400;1,700;1,900&family=Roboto:ital,wght@0,100;0,300;0,400;0,500;0,700;0,900;1,100;1,300;1,400;1,500;1,700;1,900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        @page {
            size: Letter;
            margin: 0.75in;
        }

        :root {
            --primary-color: #6A1B9A;
            --text-color: #333333;
            --light-text: #666666;
            --link-color: #7B1FA2;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Merriweather', serif;
            font-size: 10pt;
            line-height: 1.5;
            color: var(--text-color);
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }

        .header {
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--primary-color);
            padding-bottom: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            font-size: 2.2em;
            margin: 0;
            color: var(--primary-color);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        h3 {
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1.05em;
            margin: 18px 0 8px;
            color: var(--primary-color);
        }

        .contact-info {
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            margin-top: 10px;
            font-size: 0.95em;
            color: var(--light-text);
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 8px;
            align-items: center;
            white-space: nowrap;
        }

        .contact-separator {
            margin: 0 8px;
            color: #ccc;
        }

        a {
            color: var(--link-color);
            text-decoration: none;
            word-break: keep-all;
        }

        .meta-info {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .date {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .recipient {
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .subject {
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .content p {
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .content ul {
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .signature {
            margin-top: 36px;
        }

        .signature-name {
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-top: 10px;
            color: var(--primary-color);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>{{ basics.name }}</h1>
        <div class="contact-info">
            {{ basics.location }}
            <span class="contact-separator">|</span>
            <a href="mailto:{{ basics.email }}">{{ basics.email }}</a>
        </div>
        <div class="contact-info">
            <a href="https://{{ basics.linkedin }}">LinkedIn</a>
            <span class="contact-separator">|</span>
            <a href="https://{{ basics.github }}">GitHub</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="meta-info">
        <div class="date">{{ date }}</div>
        <div class="recipient">
            {{ recipient.name }}
            {% if recipient.title %}<br>{{ recipient.title }}{% endif %}
            {% if recipient.company %}<br>{{ recipient.company }}{% endif %}
            {% if recipient.address %}<br>{{ recipient.address }}{% endif %}
        </div>
        <div class="subject">Re: Application for {{ posting_title or role_title }}{% if reference_number %} (Reference {{ reference_number }}){% endif %}</div>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <p>Dear {{ recipient.name }},</p>

        <p>I am submitting my application to the {{ recipient.company or 'CSE' }} general inventory for cybersecurity analyst opportunities as they arise. I am motivated by your mission in foreign signals intelligence, cyber operations, and cyber security, and I value your focus on equity, diversity, and inclusion.</p>

        {% if interest_points %}
        <h3>Interest</h3>
        <ul>
            {% for point in interest_points %}
            <li>{{ point }}</li>
            {% endfor %}
        </ul>
        {% endif %}

        {% if requirements or public_sector is defined %}
        <h3>How I Meet the Requirements</h3>
        <ul>
            {% for item in requirements %}
            <li>{{ item }}</li>
            {% endfor %}
            {% if public_sector is defined %}
            <li>Citizenship: {{ public_sector.citizenship }}</li>
            <li>Official language: {{ public_sector.language_profile }}</li>
            <li>Security clearance: {{ public_sector.clearance }}</li>
            <li>Location: {{ public_sector.relocation }}</li>
            {% endif %}
        </ul>
        {% endif %}

        {% if assets %}
        <h3>Assets and Added Value</h3>
        <ul>
            {% for item in assets %}
            <li>{{ item }}</li>
            {% endfor %}
        </ul>
        {% endif %}

        {% if projects %}
        <h3>Selected Evidence</h3>
        <ul>
            {% for project in projects[:2] %}
            <li>
                <strong>
                    {% if project.url %}
                    <a href="{{ project.url }}" target="_blank">{{ project.title }}</a>
                    {% else %}
                    {{ project.title }}
                    {% endif %}
                </strong>: {{ project.bullets[0] }}
            </li>
            {% endfor %}
        </ul>
        {% endif %}

        <p>{{ summary }}</p>

        {% if program_eligibility is defined and program_eligibility.workbc_wage_subsidy_line %}
        <p>{{ program_eligibility.workbc_wage_subsidy_line }}</p>
        {% endif %}

        {% if public_sector is defined and public_sector.equity_statement %}
        <p>{{ public_sector.equity_statement }}</p>
        {% endif %}

        <p>Thank you for your time and consideration. I welcome the opportunity to discuss where my background aligns with your current and upcoming needs.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="signature">
        <p>Sincerely,</p>
        <div class="signature-name">{{ basics.name }}</div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
